column3: The small insulated lunch box  - MB Capsule graphic Blossom
column4: For a tasty treat at any time or place  whether a sweet or savoury snack, complete a meal or a delicious dessert  always be sure to hit the spot. column3: The 50cl bottle - MB Positive M pink Flamingo
column4:

Thats one clever 50cl bottle! 

*In accordance with the regulations

column3: The compact insulated bottle - MB Pop blue Infinity

Its compact, easy-to-carry size is ideal for all handbags or sports bags, while its 360 ml capacity is perfect for enjoying fresh juices and steaming coffees, teas and chocolates.
